1. *Pasti* mu je nogu u ponor (He fell headlong).
2. *Pasti* je u vodu (He fell into the water).
3. U prošlosti su mnogi ljudi *padali* u zablude (Many people have fallen into error in the past).
4. Ovo je izloženo da bi se izbeglo da se *padne* u zamku (This is exposed to avoid falling into a trap).
5. Oni su *pali* u oči svima (They fell into the eyes of everyone).
6. *Padne* na zemlju u nesvesti (He falls to the ground unconscious).
7. *Padam* u depresiju (I'm falling into depression).
8. Ona je *padala* u suze (She was falling into tears).